{"type": "article", "id": 13497, "title": "太阳智能采光镜", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-14T07:46:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125740ZqRzreDHtA24vKFd.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tLucy 据说是世界上第一个太阳智能采光镜，来自意大利的设计团队 Solenica。Lucy 外表是一个安置在圆形底座上面的透明球体，里面有平面镜，光传感器，太阳能电池，指示器等设备，摆放在某个位置后，可以实时跟踪太阳的轨迹，并反射在用户希望得到光亮的地方，以此来解决有些房间光照不足的问题。当把 Lucy 的“鼻子”对准天花板，可以得到散射到整个房间的光。同时，团队也在开发配合的手机 App，辅助用户照明需求。<a href=\"http://preorderlucy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141240sz7UXO8lBCtNSIdY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44376528\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141241p1ykiKEY36rHJ2nj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.30929095\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261412412kxLPaqKsOoUlgy8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39608802\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141241XrnofYKthw49JWAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141242vD1yArfw469B2xTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40464548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}